data.description: Hurry to check out this awesome 3 bedroom step-saving ranch situated on corner lot. Loads of updates within the last 3 years. Eat-in Kitchen with beautiful white cabinets, granite counter tops, range, dishwasher, and microwave, white sub-way back splash tile, and vinyl plank flooring. Adjoining is Great Room with vaulted ceilings and also with plank flooring. Down the hallway you'll find the primary Bedroom, and updated Bath with recent vanity, tub and commode. Recent light fixtures, recent replacement windows, vinyl siding, and plank vinyl flooring thru-out. Convenient attached carport. Enjoy this rural setting while close to Radcliff/ Elizabethtown, and Fort Knox!!! See if you qualify for zero downpayment!!! Does have an assumable 6.5%loan!! Don't delay call today for showing!!
